node.text:
It’s 7.30am. The sun is just peaking over the horizon. You walk towards the water... 

Are you...

- A faffer
- A plopper 
- A peace disturber 
- An everything but 
- A zen master 

Tell us in the comments below 😅👇

Filmed by @wonderfulwildwomen 

#TeamSpeedo #Speedo #Outdoorswimming

node.title: Outdoor Swimming: How do you get in?

node.text:
Great British star @elliesimmonds has today announced her retirement from competitive swimming. Ellie has won 8x Paralympic medals across four events - FIVE of them gold 🔥 She’s also won 17 medals at the World Para Swimming Championships and set numerous world record times. Ellie, thank you for being an incredible athlete. Now, as always, Speedo are so proud to have you in Team Speedo. #TeamSpeedo forever 💙 

#MakeWaves
